import pandas as pd
import pandas_ta as pta
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

In [ ]:
rsi_btc = pta.rsi(asset_history['Adj Close'],length=14).dropna()

plt.axhline(30,color='g', label='30% RSI')

plt.legend(loc='best')
